565
00:53:49,976 --> 00:54:06,320
[SPEAKER_00]: And so in talking to him and then also Sam and Nicole, depending on how cold it is outside, we could probably have lion dances and a little parade in front of the library that can enter the library and wind its way around the library, which could be fun.

566
00:54:07,400 --> 00:54:19,765
[SPEAKER_00]: Then Nicole, the children's room librarian, she was on vacation last week, so I'm working to set up a meeting with her to help figure out some children's activities.

567
00:54:19,845 --> 00:54:27,868
[SPEAKER_00]: She has all kinds of crafts and supplies, so we actually will be hosting the event.

568
