569
00:54:34,070 --> 00:54:35,891
[SPEAKER_00]: Do you have anything else to add, Frances?

570
00:54:38,008 --> 00:54:51,614
[SPEAKER_08]: Just working on an Asian bakery that could specialize in small size Asian quick bites.

571
00:54:53,474 --> 00:54:55,415
