860
01:22:52,841 --> 01:22:53,722
[SPEAKER_08]: Steve, I don't know.

861
01:22:53,742 --> 01:22:58,843
[SPEAKER_08]: That is a question that you can ask Janelle Austin when Janelle attends our meeting next month.

862
01:23:00,578 --> 01:23:02,199
[SPEAKER_08]: I will, thank you.

863
